    <p>The Bailey's Market Etsy shop carries everything that travels well: dried culinary herbs and spice blends from Honest Herbs, loose-leaf teas from Wild Kitchen, freshly milled flour and cornmeal from Stone Mill, and curated gift sets from the Harvest Collection.</p>
